      • composeDirectoryFilter

        protected static java.util.List<java.lang.String> composeDirectoryFilter(Module module)
        Junit 5 searches for tests in the classpath. When 2 modules have e.g. the same package, one depends on another, and tests have to run in single module only, by configuration settings or to avoid repetition in fork by module mode, additional filters per output directories are required.
